{"tid":450631,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個屌打中文字嘅英文字","createTime":"2017-10-28T11:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T21:20:22.000Z","uid":12622,"like":0,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"679f799bd062ac3133440c26bac7f264e9fcd046","tid":450631,"uid":12622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:21:01.000Z","msg":"中文嗰 &quot;我&quot; 字<br />\n根本好似幼稚園啲細路仔喺度鬼畫符<br />\n又橫又竪又撇又點，亂鳩嚟<br />\n小一第一次學喱隻字嗰陣已經覺得極難理解<br />\n都唔知整喱個字嗰條友點解會諗到俾人用依隻字稱呼自己<br />\n你估個個都好似你咁扭曲咩<br />\n同時都反映咗嗰種迂迴曲折嘅文化<br />\n好聽啲就叫含蓄囉<br />\n唔似鬼佬咁，直腸直肚，爽快！<br />\n棟一畫 &quot;I&quot; 字就搞掂<br />\n同埋就算比老師罰抄&quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">I</span>以後唔會欠交功課&quot;都唔使咁辛苦<br />\n<br />\n預咗比教中文嘅徐老師屌<br />\n你唔妥我嘅，或者講吓屌打英文字嘅中文字都得<br />\n但我就無咁得閒理你，我要開始做住啲罰抄先"},{"pid":"e484d0530b4ad75837e766cc928ec0c77755bec1","tid":450631,"uid":76366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:25:45.000Z","msg":"返去做功課啦小朋友"},{"pid":"b90eae5967dce0f21319e5417e5a37f2db8e3a91","tid":450631,"uid":49258,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:27:12.000Z","msg":"有見地呀, <br />\n咁點解唔全部用英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4a73f694f0fcb2c6e42c54662668220ffaa65f","tid":450631,"uid":135132,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:31:31.000Z","msg":"你唔講埋I的變化型Me, My, Mine?"},{"pid":"a1e837faa5991a07ec19a58fe6151002df1aba33","tid":450631,"uid":53254,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:33:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔講埋I的變化型Me, My, Mine?</blockquote><br />\n樓主淨係識I, 唔好踢爆佢"},{"pid":"bdfc7a3f956be1dc7f2ab1259a1863c7bc2db75c","tid":450631,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:38:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你唔講埋I的變化型Me, My, Mine?</blockquote><br />\n樓主淨係識I, 唔好踢爆佢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoj